==English==
===Etymology===
''[[mucosa]]'' (mucus membrane) + ''[[-itis]]'' (inflammation)
===Noun===
'''mucositis'''
# A [[complication]] of some [[cancer]] [[therapy|therapies]] in which the lining of the [[digestive system]] becomes [[inflammation|inflamed]]. Often seen as [[sore]]s in the [[mouth]].
